{"tid":1963812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門政府同時宣布：向合資格僱員派1.5萬　企業最多獲發20萬","createTime":"2020-04-08T11:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:11:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a139a431bd43a0e3924a0ab3870ceeee77099a86","tid":1963812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1519606_2_L_20200408190205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1519606_2_L_20200408190205.jpg&h=b3f52606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519606-20200408.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519606-20200408.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=6f0ed922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519606-20200408.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=66e4d314\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519606-20200408.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n澳門公布一百億元抗疫援助專項基金內容，支援受疫情影響的企業及僱員，合資格僱員將獲發一次性15000元，每名居民亦會有再多5000元的電子消費卡，自由工作者亦會有一次性10000元援助。<br />\n<br />\n合資格企業可按僱員人數，獲發一次性15000至20萬元款項，持有多間商號的同一納稅人，可獲最多100萬元援助。<br />\n<br />\n經濟財政司司長李偉農表示，期望透過措施，盡快及用最大努力紓解民困，增強社會信心，團結穩定社會。"},{"pid":"6b244b46dd5d0cfeb145a8385161968bc2438fbb","tid":1963812,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"澳共睇住港共嚟打<br />\n<br />\n澳門個新特首真係唔講得少！"},{"pid":"01fae8e9c45d8e0213cff7dbdb0b07a397a294d6","tid":1963812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"仆街, 早知去澳門開多間！"},{"pid":"765c2196760cc8e3feff16a024a4cd65c0fabf7f","tid":1963812,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"高下立見 <img src=\"/asse